---
import CodeBlock from '../CodeBlock.astro';
import CommentBlock from '../CommentBlock.astro';
import SectionHeader from '../SectionHeader.astro';
---
<section id="problem" aria-labelledby="problem-title">
  <div class="container">
    <SectionHeader eyebrow="01 / Problem" title="The glue is the problem." />

    <div class="problem">
      <div class="problem__copy">
        <p>Multi-agent systems coordinate today through ad-hoc message buses, shared memory, or scrollback chat logs that no one can audit later. Every team rebuilds the same plumbing, badly.</p>
        <p>Documents and code — the actual artifacts under negotiation — sit on the side, disconnected from the trail of decisions that produced them.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="compare">
        <div>
          <div class="compare__label">// the usual: hand-rolled glue</div>
          <CodeBlock lang="markdown" filename="spec.md">
            <Fragment set:html={`<span class="tk-hd"># spec.md</span>

<span class="tk-com">&lt;!-- TODO eduardo: should the column be by name or index? --&gt;</span>
<span class="tk-com">&lt;!-- planner @ 14:32: name. update --&gt;</span>
<span class="tk-com">&lt;!-- engineer @ 14:35: ack --&gt;</span>

<span class="tk-hd">## API</span>
The CLI sorts a CSV by a column...`} />
          </CodeBlock>
        </div>

        <div>
          <div class="compare__label">// remargin: one threaded comment</div>
          <CommentBlock size="sm" label="remargin comment">
            <Fragment slot="header">
              <span class="k">id</span>       <span class="v"><span class="v--id">abc</span></span>
              <span class="k">author</span>   <span class="v v--success">eduardo</span>
              <span class="k">type</span>     <span class="v v--success">human</span>
              <span class="k">ts</span>       <span class="v v--mono">2026-05-19T14:32:00-04:00</span>
              <span class="k">reply-to</span> <span class="v"><span class="v--id">jl1</span></span>
              <span class="k">ack</span>      <span class="v v--ack">planner@14:35</span>
            </Fragment>
            <p>Should the column be addressed by <strong>name</strong> or <strong>index</strong>? Picking <em>name</em> — updating the spec.</p>
          </CommentBlock>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.problem {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 40fr) minmax(0, 60fr);
  gap: 48px;
  align-items: start;
}
@media (max-width: 900px) { .problem { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 32px; } }

.problem__copy :global(p) { color: var(--color-text-muted); max-width: 50ch; }
.problem__copy :global(p + p) { margin-top: 12px; }

.compare { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }
.compare__label {
  font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 12px; color: var(--color-text-dim);
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
</style>
